{
  "texts": [
    "However, this architecture makes it very difficult to understand the causality behind the examined physical process.",
    "As our goal is to move toward a unified spatio-temporal hazard model, causality may not be a fundamental requirement at this stage.",
    "However, we envision future efforts to be directed toward more interpretable and causal machine or deep learning.",
    "Ultimately, more can be done to clarify how our ENN should and should not be used, at least in its present form.",
    "For instance, with the current or even higher temporal frequency, our output could be used as part of parametric insurances (Horton, 2018) or large-scale risk reduction planning (Prabhakar et al., 2009)."
  ]
}